  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "You should be able to send a transaction with a gas price lower than the current base fee. That transaction then would be kept in the mempool until the base fee is low enough for it to be mined.\r\n\r\nI think the reason this is not working right now is that `eth_estimateGas` is throwing when the transaction has a gas price lower than the base fee.\r\n\r\nRelated:\r\n- https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/issues/3474",
